longBusinessSummary: iWallet Corporation designs, develops, manufactures, and sells personal security products to protect against identity, personal, and financial information theft in the United States and internationally. The company offers biometric locking luxury storage cases that protect cash, credit cards, and personal information with a proprietary fingerprint security system. It intends to serve customers in luxury secure storage cases and accessories markets. The company was founded in 2009 and is based in San Diego, California.
